Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working hard today, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're wearing proper clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The master has guests today,\Nso I'm wearing a uniform, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Clothes like this make\Nme feel really stiff, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to follow all of the\Nconfining rules in the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I've decided\Nto continue on this path...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! It's about time to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't hear you, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the view I want to see is next to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because views I haven't\Nseen before are waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ryu! It's time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, did she... with the whistle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.25,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10: Inexperienced Heart, Going Deeper"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For calling Ryu for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Red hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rare. It's my first time seeing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how you can get\Nthe bird to fly with your whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person\NI've talked to since arriving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally feel less nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some business... I have an\Naudience with the second prince after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With Prince Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the master's guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing. Will you hear me out?\NI don't want to be alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm in the middle of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just for a little bit, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost break time, anyway.\NI'll go back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an apprentice court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kihal Toghrul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with formalities,\Nso you can just call me Kihal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's my friend, Popo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a beautiful bird.\NIt's my first time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised Popo, but on the island where I live,\Nthere's a whole flock living in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\NI've heard of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,People who live with birds on\None of Clarines' southern islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You live with the birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since my great-grandfather's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds we live with are\Nthe same species as Popo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When they spread their blue and green wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,they're beautiful! Like the sea is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds have really good hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and they find the mineral ores\Nin the ocean near the island
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,by listening to the sound\Nthey make in the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They tell us where schools of fish are, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're always together\Nwhen we go out on the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mineral ore\Nfrom the ocean, the walnut stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they're polished, they become shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The whistle from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes down to it, the island\Nis part of someone else's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened a year and a half ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The lord who had just inherited\Nthe lands brought his noble friends
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and started to hunt the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The lord did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. His friends loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds' feathers were rare and\Ncould be sold at a high price, they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was even praised\Nwith words I loathe to recount.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Popo was also the target of\Na hunt and was seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've asked them to stop many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But they wouldn't listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The lord then said, "I'll let you\Nmeet the prince, so you can ask him."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I ask, it's not like he'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll just laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with high rank won't\Nlisten to those with no rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how I would\Ndescribe Prince Zen's character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?\NHe's nobility! Royalty, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Even so, I had to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupting your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I have to go back soon, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I stay here until the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to make it illegal to hunt the birds
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and make Yuris Island a nature reserve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will consider it and\Ngive my decision tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, from what I have heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe this should be discussed\Namong the concerned parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brecker of Yuris Island\Nand its resident, Kihal Toghrul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, I apologize for troubling you\Nwith a matter I could not resolve myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand now, don't you, Toghrul?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihal, I have prepared a room for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the concerned parties should discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good will come of you worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are herbs protected\Nbecause of their efficacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If the birds also had\Nsomething special to offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the birds are important\Nto the residents of the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't matter to the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's enjoying hunting with\Nhis friends on his own land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The mineral ore on the island, the walnut stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't really something that\Ncan be sold for much, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is say that it is\Nwithin the rights of the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brecker brought this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it appears to be\Na decorative arrow souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably believes his own values are\Ncommon sense and doesn't question them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the viscount bring this up\Nto you in the first place, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because the previous\Nviscount and I met a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time meeting Brecker, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you're being used, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shut up.\N--Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say it, too, Kiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I hate that I cannot help that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, there's something\NI want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihal, is it true that with\Na signal from your whistle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get the bird to fly where you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Everyone who has gone\Nthrough training on the island can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you have the bird fly somewhere far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We often send them out\Nto fishing boats in the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they know where the boat is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bells made from walnut stones\Neach have a unique sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These birds can tell the\Nslight difference between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If they hear the sound of the bell in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they will land where they hear that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I would like to look into using\Nthat as a means of communication in Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from a certain person
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that perhaps the ability to control\Nthe birds could be used for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured, if they can be used for\Ncommunication, it would benefit the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was definitely worth investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'd like to test it over a long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Test...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll test to see if it's\Nsomething we can make use of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, at the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, may I name the\Nperson who will hold the bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please! It might be a bother,\Nbut to me, the castle is still the enemy camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy camp...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a proposal from the kingdom,\NI can't really trust it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have faith in Prince Zen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then I want to work with you\Nso maybe I can feel that way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The test will be as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To a point ten kilometers west of the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,at a lakeside watchtower that\Nwould take 40 minutes by horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the bird will sent bearing a document.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The person at the watchtower\Nwill receive the document,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sign it, attach the bell,\Nand send the bird back to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This will all occur within 25 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If all the conditions are met,\Nit will be acknowledged;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if not, it will be regarded as a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To go and come back from the lake in 25 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.\NIt's a bird that's going, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The bird handler will be Kihal Toghrul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Assisting her will be Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Three soldiers and a messenger\Nwill accompany her to the watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A red-haired girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why something so\Noutrageous was brought up suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To get the prince's friend on your side--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a clever one, Toghrul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we are looking to see\Nif this proposal will benefit Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to judge for\Nyourself as a lord of this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, your highness, I would also like to\Naccompany them to the lakeside watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not that I am suspicious of anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but if those girls act dishonestly in any way,\Nit would reflect badly on you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Brecker, Shirayuki and the\Nothers will head to the lakeside watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The bird will be sent at four o'clock,\Nand the test will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sound, Popo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting, okay, Kihal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Shirayuki should\Nbe waiting by the lake by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Kihal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let the test begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Popo. Shirayuki's\Nwaiting for you in the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a clear sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go outside to wait now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful view.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I like high places with a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there are things\Nyou can't see when you're low.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a little about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an apprentice of sorts at the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're the prince's friend,\Nwithout any kind of social status,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,there are things that must be hard to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't attend parties\Nor balls where nobles gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so of course there will be discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Prince Zen can continue\Nto associate with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I will support you from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, I want this test to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The bird did not come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The bird will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you are planning on refusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! What good will it be if it fails?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay inside until time runs out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! Does a mere soldier like\Nyou dare to speak up against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open up, Lord Brecker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think will happen\Nif those island people and birds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,became beneficial to the kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm so stupid that\NI wouldn't notice that possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and would just let you do what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's noisy up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a piece of cake to keep a soldier quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use crying to the prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how he actually feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't do something so stupid\Nas to believe you over me, his subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and risk antagonizing those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, that's what it means\Nto be of different social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What you say is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there are times when\Nwe can't act on how we really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, then I will do all\NI can to make sure that doesn't happen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What can someone like you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the status of one who can't see the\Neffort of someone trying to protect something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...is lower than this watchtower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell fell into the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't find it and ring it,\NPopo won't land here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this the viscount's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... from this height...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you decided to side with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one working for Prince Zen\Nwho could hear her words and ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Popo's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it flew away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, around where did it fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A little ways out from where I jumped in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still no sign of the bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Popo... Shirayuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Popo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that bird trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds have really good hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and they find the mineral ores\Nin the ocean near the island
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,by listening to the sound\Nthey make in the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more minutes before time runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost been 25 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it not work, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To make a bird fly with just a sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot hear the sound of the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Popo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The document and the bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have confirmed the signatures\Nof everyone. There is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to bring in the bird\Nhandlers as a means of communication!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Popo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a report along with the signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, Kiki! Ready the horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have arrested the\Nviscount due to his interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing by at the watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The assistant was injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When the viscount asked to\Naccompany the group to the watchtower,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Prince Zen would refuse,\Nbut he dared to allow him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed obvious that the viscount was\Nplanning to use Shirayuki for his own gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have believed in the soldiers\Nand that girl and left it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How will he protect what he wants to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably hasn't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back. Take care of my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, if you're looking\Nfor Shirayuki, she's upstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki said that if there were times\Nyou couldn't act on your true feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then she would make sure\Nthat didn't happen to you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Zen, sorry...\NBut I wasn't going to hide it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you'd get mad if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you and Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.98,0:24:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Calmly... So no one will\Nthink anything is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.69,0:24:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.19,0:24:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some time to think by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.73,0:24:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:20.16,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 11: Encountering...\NA Color for the First Time"
